<h3 id="discovery">Discovery</h3>

<p>While the individual products in the Amp portfolio are in highly competitive areas, there were much fewer competitors for Amp itself. Competitors on the whole were hard to differentiate between in a sea of blue gradients. My initial workshop and discovery looked for an opportunity to be more expressive, to cut through the noise, and differentiate . To position it as something energising, direct and empowering.</p>

