    </div>
</section>

<h3 id="north-star">North Star</h3>

<p>The products in the Amp portfolio are in highly competitive areas individually, but there were much fewer competitors for Amp itself. Eyeing cross sell and bundling opportuniteis, Amp wanted to have more presence on the individual product level. Competitors on the whole were hard to differentiate between, mainly being modern but reserved. There was an opportunity to be more expressive to cut through the noise. To position it as something energising, direct and empowering.</p>

